org.nerd4j.csv.conf.mapping.xml

Class XMLHandlerConf

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nerd4j.csv.conf.mapping.xml.XMLHandlerConf
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.nerd4j.dependency.DependentBean
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    XMLReaderConf, XMLWriterConf

    public class XMLHandlerConf
extends Object
implements org.nerd4j.dependency.DependentBean
    Abstract common representation of an XML configuration for objects able to handle CSV. This class implements the DependentBean interface that allows dependencies to be automatically resolved.
    Author:
    Nerd4j Team
